      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented version control, regression testing, and traceable release history consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 19.2 was used. Version control documentation, regression test suite results, and release notes were reviewed. All SQA artifacts meet the Gradation 2 threshold for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
