      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification benchmarks must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations for incompressible viscous flow at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Standard lid-driven cavity and Poiseuille flow benchmarks were executed. Numerical solutions converged to analytical references within accepted tolerances, confirming Gradation 2 code verification."
    },
    {
