      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be computed on at least three systematically refined meshes; GCI < 5% on QOI (hemolysis index).",
      "rationale": "Three hexahedral meshes (2.1M, 6.8M, 18.4M cells) were generated. Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI of 2.3% on the hemolysis index, exceeding the Gradation 2 requirement and satisfying Gradation 3."
